{"id":6361,"date":"2012-09-13T22:15:57","date_gmt":"2012-09-14T02:15:57","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=6361"},"modified":"2023-10-05T21:04:54","modified_gmt":"2023-10-05T17:04:54","slug":"scatter-hasanat-transgressors","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/13\/scatter-hasanat-transgressors\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Sin: Allah scatters good deeds of transgressors"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Thawban reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>I certainly know people from my nation who will come on the Day of Resurrection with good deeds like the mountains of Tihamah, but Allah will &#8216;scatter them like dust,&#8217;<\/strong>\u201d (25:23). Thawban said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, describe them to us and tell us more, that we will not become like them.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>They are your brothers and from your ethnicity, taking up worship at night as you do, but they will be people who transgress the sacred limits of Allah when they are alone.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4245<\/p>\n<p>Grade:\u00a0<strong><em>Sahih\u00a0<\/em><\/strong>(authentic) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062b\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064b\u0627 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0651\u062a\u0650\u064a \u064a\u064e\u0623\u0652\u062a\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e \u064a\u064e\u064